319
00:51:39.423 --> 00:51:40.958
POLITIE KOPENHAGEN

320
00:51:49.465 --> 00:51:51.381
Hier is het.

321
00:52:06.381 --> 00:52:09.006
Mama, ik ben er. 
Met Astrid Ericsson.

322
00:52:16.506 --> 00:52:19.715
Marie.
